data.description: Enjoy the peace and quiet without being far from town, this 3 bed 2 ba home on 5 acres. With 2 decks – one overlooking the backyard and one on the front side of the house overlooking the trees and the hills towards Fayetteville. Each room has large windows with wood slatted blinds, pergo wood flooring in all but one bedroom (remainder of pergo will stay), tile in the kitchen and dining area and large closets in the bedrooms. The wood stove is wonderful in winter and there are ceiling fans in each room. There is a two car carport with a small shed attached, freestanding shed with insulation and electricity, flagstone steps to the fire pit, vegetable bed set up and lots of shade trees.
